Support
Conjurer's Pursuit;;1;Every 3 Regeneration Globes gathered grants an extra +0.25 Mana per second, permanently.
Overload;;1;Increases the damage of Psionic Storm by 20%.
Psi-Infusion;;1;Psionic Storm returns 5 Mana for each target initally hit.
Minion Bulwark;;1;Plasma Shield amount is increased 50% on Minions and Mercenaries and lasts forever.
Mental Acuity (Trait);;4;Reduces the cooldown of Oracle by 10 seconds.
Leeching Plasma;;4;While Plasma Shield is active, 20% of the target's Basic Attack damage is returned as Health.
Reinforce Structure;;4;Plasma Shield is 100% stronger and lasts 100% longer when cast on Structures.
Promote;;4;Activate to give target allied lane Minion +300% permanent Health and +100% permanent damage. Has 2 charges. 60s cooldown.
Healing Ward;;4;Activate to place a ward on the ground that heals allies in an area for 3.12% of their max Health every second for 10 seconds. 60s cooldown.
Khala's Embrace;;7;If Plasma Shield expires, 50% of the Shield remains indefinitely. This effect does not stack.
Static Charge;;7;Enemies damaged by Psionic Storm are marked with Static Charge. Your Basic Attacks consume the Static Charge to deal 40 damage.
Deep Shift;;7;Dimensional Shift duration increased by 0.75 seconds.
Calldown: MULE;;7;Activate to calldown a Mule that repairs Structures, one at a time, near target point for 60 seconds, healing for 100 Health every 1 second. Grants 1 ammo every 5 seconds. 60s cooldown.
Force Wall;;10;Create a wall that blocks all units from moving through it for 2.5 seconds. 12s cooldown.
Archon;;10;Transform into an Archon, gaining a 200 point Shield, causing Basic Attacks to deal 64 damage and splash for 32 additional damage. Lasts for 15 seconds. 100s cooldown.
Distortion Beam;;13;Basic Attacks slow enemies by 25% for 1.5 seconds.
Prescience;;13;Dimensional Shift will automatically activate when you fall below 15% Health. This effect has a separate 60 second cooldown.
Scryer (Trait);;13;Oracle duration increased by 3 seconds and grants 15% increased Movement Speed.
Spell Shield;;13;Upon taking Ability Damage, reduce all Ability Damage taken by 50% for 2 seconds. Can only trigger once every 30 seconds.
Shrink Ray;;13;Activate to reduce an enemy Hero's damage by 50% and Movement Speed by 50% for 4 seconds. 60s cooldown.
Evasive Shielding;;16;The target of your Plasma Shield also gains 25% Movement Speed for 4 seconds.
Resonation;;16;Psionic Storm targets are slowed by 25% for 1 second.
Second Strike;;16;After casting Psionic Storm, you may cast Psionic Storm again for free within 3 seconds. The damage does not stack.
Dimensional Warp;;16;While Dimensional Shifted, gain 50% Movement Speed and heal for 40 Health.
Resurgence of the Storm;;20;Upon dying, revive back at your Altar after 5 seconds. This can occur once every 120 seconds.
Storm Shield;;20;Activate to give all nearby allied Heroes a Shield for 20% of their max Health for 3 seconds. 45s cooldown.
Force Barrier;;20;Force Wall range increased by 50% and duration by 1 second.
Twilight Archon;;20;Archon initial shield amount increased by 50%. Basic Attacks deal 50% more damage and gain 3 range.